<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3690">أَبُو صَفْوَانَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ بْنِ يَزِيدَ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">عُرْوَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/539">أُسَامَةَ بْنِ زَيْدٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> رَكِبَ عَلَى حِمَارٍ عَلَى إِكَافٍ عَلَيْهِ قَطِيفَةٌ وَأَرْدَفَ أُسَامَةَ وَرَاءَهُ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>